    <title type="html"><![CDATA[xUtils在开发过程中DbUtils的使用]]></title>
    <link href="http://xupingwei.github.io/blog/2015/12/13/02/"/>
    <updated>2015-12-13T17:18:56+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://xupingwei.github.io/blog/2015/12/13/02</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>xUtils在开发过程中DbUtils的使用</h1>

<h3>1.DbUtils中的save的用法</h3>

<h5>1）根据官网save的方法很好用</h5>

<ul>
<li>dbUtils.save(userDetails);</li>
<li>userDetails：实体类的对象&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;直接调用save方法进行保存，很容易不再啰嗦</li>
</ul>


<h3>2.DbUtils中的update的用法</h3>

<h5>1）update用法</h5>

<ul>
<li>在调用dbUtils.update(&hellip;)时，有时会出现NOT FOUND &ldquo;id"的错误&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-这是因为在执行update方法时，传入的参数出现错误</li>
<li>正确的用法是：</li>
</ul>


<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>代码 </span><a href='http://xupingwei.github.io/'>链接 </a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>dbUtils.update(
</span><span class='line'>      userDetails,WhereBuilder.b(
</span><span class='line'>      "phone", "=", userDetails.getPhone()), 
</span><span class='line'>      "avatarname","username","gender", "birthday", 
</span><span class='line'>      "business", "grade", "city", "area", "address", 
</span><span class='line'>      "progress");</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>userDetails:需要跟新的实体类对象</li>
<li>&ldquo;phone"：根据表中的列名称进行跟新</li>
<li>userDetails.getPhone():称更新实体类对象的唯一值</li>
<li>&ldquo;avatarname"，"username"：需要更新的列名称</li>
</ul>


<h3>3.DbUtils中的find的用法：</h3>

<h5>1) findFirst用法</h5>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>代码 </span><a href='http://xupingwei.github.io/'>链接 </a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>lastTime = dbUtils.findFirst(
</span><span class='line'>  Selector.from(UserDetails.class)
</span><span class='line'>          .where(WhereBuilder.b(
</span><span class='line'>              "lastmodifytime", "=", time)));</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>Selector.from(UserDetails.class)：查找哪张表（这里查找的是UserDetails这张表）</li>
<li>WhereBuilder.b(&ldquo;lastmodifytime&rdquo;, &ldquo;=&rdquo;, time)：条件查询</li>
</ul>


<h5>2）findAll用法</h5>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>代码</span><a href='http://xupingwei.github.io/'>链接 </a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>mList = dbUtils.findAll(UserDetails.class);</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h5>3) findDbModelFirst</h5>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>代码</span><a href='http://xupingwei.github.io/'>链接 </a></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>dbUtils.findDbModelFirst(
</span><span class='line'>      Selector.from(Category.class)
</span><span class='line'>              .select(new String[]{"lastupdate"}));</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<ul>
<li>DbModel&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-相当于表的一个视图，把其当做视图看待</li>
<li>select(new String[]{&ldquo;lastupdate&rdquo;})&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-这个视图中包含的属性，这里包含的属性是“lastupdate”</li>
<li>如果需要包含其他的属性，直接在new String[]{}里增加表的字段</li>
</ul>

]]></content>
